Python Number Guessing Game

Goal: Create a game where the computer randomly picks a number 
and the user has to try and guess the correct number. 

Things to be included:
1) The user inputs the max number the cpu can user
2) The score increase from 0 for every wrong guess
3) With every wrong guess, the cpu will give a hint
4) Validate the input is a number
5) If the same number is inputted more than once, a penalty point will be added.
6) It will be a console based game
7) It will loop through and ask the user to play again

Clues: 
1) The clues will included higher or lower than previous guess
2) what numbers it can be divided and multipled by


